      "reason": "Exception: Timezone is a LiteralKit union over the generated IANA tzdb enumeration; example-based assertions cover representative decode and rejection, and property sampling over a finite literal union only re-picks already-enumerated members, so schema-derived property coverage would be vacuous."
    },
